      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "V{\\'e}rifier que $C_n^kC_k^p = C_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}$ pour $p \\le k \\le n$.",
        "html": "<p>V<span>é</span>rifier que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(C_n^kC_k^p =\nC_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}\\)</span> pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p \\le k \\le\nn\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "73066db0-ef22-4b5d-b965-fec8a4e8f7b4",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{k=0}^n \\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n\n\\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
