      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire $\\sum_{k=0}^n (-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0$ si $p < n$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n\n(-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt;\nn\\)</span>.</p>\n"
